{"id":424130,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/01/非新闻-2015年中国群体事件统计/","date":"2016-01-06T07:10:54Z","modified":"2016-01-06T07:10:54Z","title":"非新闻 | 2015年中国群体事件统计","content":"<p>2015年记录到群体游行、示威、集会等共计28950起，平均每天79起，比2014年增长了34%，主要增长群体来自与房地产相关的工人和业主，此外，投资人、商户以及环境保护相关群体的增长也比较明显。主要增长地区在河南、河北、江苏等省。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424131\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818595459_85660ae39c_o-1024x589.jpg\" alt=\"23818595459_85660ae39c_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818595459_85660ae39c_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818595459_85660ae39c_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818595459_85660ae39c_o-768x441.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>被镇压和被抓捕</p>\n<p>至少1943起遭到警察镇压（有示威者被抓捕），至少14250人被抓捕。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424132\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559611713_6b267519a9_o.jpg\" alt=\"23559611713_6b267519a9_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559611713_6b267519a9_o.jpg 1742w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559611713_6b267519a9_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559611713_6b267519a9_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559611713_6b267519a9_o-1024x588.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>地区</p>\n<p>河南、广东、河北、江苏等排名前十的省份占总数的64%。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424133\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o.jpg\" alt=\"24078361292_59ac35570e_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o-300x191.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o-768x490.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o-1024x653.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>年底（2月份）讨薪高峰主要发生在河南、河北、安徽、江苏、四川以及湖北，广东相比平时有所下降。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424134\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818595139_e0d306107b_o.jpg\" alt=\"23818595139_e0d306107b_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818595139_e0d306107b_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818595139_e0d306107b_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818595139_e0d306107b_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818595139_e0d306107b_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>群体</p>\n<p>工人、业主、农民占了总数的69%，工人、业主增长明显。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424135\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o-1.jpg\" alt=\"24078361292_59ac35570e_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o-1.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o-1-300x191.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o-1-768x490.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361292_59ac35570e_o-1-1024x653.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424137\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361112_490227fd84_o.jpg\" alt=\"24078361112_490227fd84_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361112_490227fd84_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361112_490227fd84_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361112_490227fd84_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24078361112_490227fd84_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（01）工人：绝大部分是建筑工人，制造、加工、服务业工人占一小部分，国企工人极少。引发示威的原因主要是欠薪，其他原因有失业赔偿、搬迁赔偿、低薪、克扣工资、欠缴社保等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424139\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890786020_0d3a17492c_o.jpg\" alt=\"23890786020_0d3a17492c_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890786020_0d3a17492c_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890786020_0d3a17492c_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890786020_0d3a17492c_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890786020_0d3a17492c_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（02）业主：楼盘、小区房产的所有者以及已购买了但未收房的准业主，引发示威的原因主要是楼盘烂尾、开发商不能按时交房、开发商欺诈销售、房屋质量差、物业乱收费、物业不作为、强拆以及环境被（或面临）污染破坏等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424141\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818594959_3746192784_o.jpg\" alt=\"23818594959_3746192784_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818594959_3746192784_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818594959_3746192784_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818594959_3746192784_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818594959_3746192784_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（03）农民：引发原因主要是强征、强拆、官员贪腐以及环境被（或面临）污染破坏等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424142\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214984_9bdce02750_o.jpg\" alt=\"23558214984_9bdce02750_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214984_9bdce02750_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214984_9bdce02750_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214984_9bdce02750_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214984_9bdce02750_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（04）死者家属：医疗事故、交通事故以及警察滥用暴力等事件中死者的家属、亲属，引发原因主要是寻求公道、要求赔偿、要求处罚事件责任人等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424144\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785890_4301600249_o.jpg\" alt=\"23890785890_4301600249_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785890_4301600249_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785890_4301600249_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785890_4301600249_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785890_4301600249_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（05）投资人：融资公司以及P2P网贷平台倒闭、跑路事件中的受害人，引发原因是不能兑付投资款和利息。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424146\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785860_11216ea5e0_o.jpg\" alt=\"23890785860_11216ea5e0_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785860_11216ea5e0_o.jpg 1736w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785860_11216ea5e0_o-300x173.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785860_11216ea5e0_o-768x442.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23890785860_11216ea5e0_o-1024x590.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（06）商户：各种实体经营场所的商家，引发原因主要租金上涨、经营困难要求减租、强拆以及物业乱收费和不作为等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424147\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24103796551_ceb2a077ca_o.jpg\" alt=\"24103796551_ceb2a077ca_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24103796551_ceb2a077ca_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24103796551_ceb2a077ca_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24103796551_ceb2a077ca_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24103796551_ceb2a077ca_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（07）拆迁户：被政府强拆了房屋的房主，引发原因是赔偿过低或没有赔偿。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424148\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214654_aa205a01d5_o.jpg\" alt=\"23558214654_aa205a01d5_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214654_aa205a01d5_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214654_aa205a01d5_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214654_aa205a01d5_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214654_aa205a01d5_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（08）出租车：引发原因主要有黑车、专车抢走客源，以及规费（份子钱）过高、政府强行收回运营权、要求涨运价等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424149\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214434_ccac807f13_o.jpg\" alt=\"23558214434_ccac807f13_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214434_ccac807f13_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214434_ccac807f13_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214434_ccac807f13_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214434_ccac807f13_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（09）家长：未成年人的监护人，引发原因主要有争取教育平权、环境等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424150\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214174_61b678fb3b_o.jpg\" alt=\"23558214174_61b678fb3b_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214174_61b678fb3b_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214174_61b678fb3b_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214174_61b678fb3b_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23558214174_61b678fb3b_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（10）教师：引发原因有欠薪、被克扣工资、低薪、欠缴社保等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424151\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559610423_1d0938e868_o.jpg\" alt=\"23559610423_1d0938e868_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559610423_1d0938e868_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559610423_1d0938e868_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559610423_1d0938e868_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23559610423_1d0938e868_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（11）路人：非事件的受害人，愿意为公义挺身而出的人，引发原因有城管暴力、警察暴力等。（2014年4月浙江温州苍南城管事件以后，很少再有因城管暴力引发的大规模事件了。）</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424153\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593969_7ff104d906_o.jpg\" alt=\"23818593969_7ff104d906_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593969_7ff104d906_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593969_7ff104d906_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593969_7ff104d906_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593969_7ff104d906_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（12）车主：车辆质量问题的受害者，引发原因主要是车商拒绝对问题车做出赔偿或赔偿标准过低。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424155\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24160307296_f44b81c277_o.jpg\" alt=\"24160307296_f44b81c277_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24160307296_f44b81c277_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24160307296_f44b81c277_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24160307296_f44b81c277_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/24160307296_f44b81c277_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（13）退伍军人：引发原因主要是退伍后待遇、福利太低或被克扣等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424156\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593509_59df62f05b_o.jpg\" alt=\"23818593509_59df62f05b_o\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593509_59df62f05b_o.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593509_59df62f05b_o-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593509_59df62f05b_o-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/23818593509_59df62f05b_o-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（14）公交车：引发原因有低薪、运价低等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424158\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/公交车.jpg\" alt=\"公交车\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/公交车.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/公交车-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/公交车-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/公交车-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（15）客运车：长途运客车辆，引发原因有运价低、被黑车抢走客源、运营权被政府强行收回等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424159\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/客运车.jpg\" alt=\"客运车\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/客运车.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/客运车-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/客运车-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/客运车-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（16）学生：引发原因主要有学校饭菜差、校方封闭管理谋取私利、负责人卷款跑路等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424165\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/学生.jpg\" alt=\"学生\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/学生.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/学生-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/学生-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/学生-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（17）三轮车：载客运营的三轮车，引发原因主要有被政府禁止载客运营、被禁止在城区通行等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424161\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/三轮车-1.jpg\" alt=\"三轮车\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/三轮车-1.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/三轮车-1-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/三轮车-1-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/三轮车-1-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/三轮车-1-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><br />\n（18）医护：医生和护士，引发原因主要有低薪、欠薪、医院改制等。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424166\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医护.jpg\" alt=\"医护\" width=\"600\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医护.jpg 1740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医护-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医护-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医护-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（19）通讯用户：中国移动、联通的客户，引发原因是商业欺诈。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424163\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/通讯用户.jpg\" alt=\"通讯用户\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/通讯用户.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/通讯用户-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/通讯用户-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/通讯用户-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/通讯用户-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><br />\n（20）失独者：失去独子的计生受害者，引发原因主要是要求政府兑现承诺，对失独者作出赔偿。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424162\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失独者.jpg\" alt=\"失独者\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失独者.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失独者-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失独者-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失独者-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失独者-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（21）专车：引发原因有被运管“钓鱼”、与出租车之间的冲突。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424167\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/专车.jpg\" alt=\"专车\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/专车.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/专车-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/专车-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/专车-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/专车-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（22）信徒：基督教、天主教的信徒，引发原因主要是政府强拆教堂。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424164\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/信徒.jpg\" alt=\"信徒\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/信徒.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/信徒-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/信徒-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/信徒-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/信徒-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><br />\n原因</p>\n<p>欠薪、商业欺诈占总数的一半。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424173\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因.jpg\" alt=\"原因\" width=\"600\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因-300x175.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因-1024x597.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424174\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因对比.jpg\" alt=\"原因对比\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因对比.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因对比-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因对比-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因对比-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/原因对比-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（01）欠薪：涉及工人、教师、医护。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424195\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠薪.jpg\" alt=\"欠薪\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠薪.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠薪-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠薪-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠薪-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠薪-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（02）商业欺诈：涉及业主、商户、通讯用户。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424199\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/商业欺诈.jpg\" alt=\"商业欺诈\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/商业欺诈.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/商业欺诈-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/商业欺诈-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/商业欺诈-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/商业欺诈-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（03）强征：涉及农民。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424197\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强征.jpg\" alt=\"强征\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强征.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强征-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强征-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强征-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强征-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（04）环境：环境被污染、破坏或面临被污染、破坏，涉及农民、业主、家长。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424191\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/环境.jpg\" alt=\"环境\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/环境.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/环境-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/环境-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/环境-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/环境-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（05）融资诈骗：融资公司倒闭、跑路、不能兑付本金等，涉及投资人。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424198\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/融资诈骗.jpg\" alt=\"融资诈骗\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/融资诈骗.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/融资诈骗-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/融资诈骗-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/融资诈骗-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/融资诈骗-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（06）强拆：涉及农民、拆迁户、信徒、商户。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424196\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强拆.jpg\" alt=\"强拆\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强拆.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强拆-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强拆-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强拆-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/强拆-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（07）物业：小区、商城的物业管理公司乱收费、不作为，涉及业主、商户。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424202\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/物业.jpg\" alt=\"物业\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/物业.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/物业-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/物业-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/物业-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/物业-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（08）医疗事故：医院过失导致病人死亡，涉及死者家属。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424203\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医疗事故.jpg\" alt=\"医疗事故\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医疗事故.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医疗事故-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医疗事故-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医疗事故-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/医疗事故-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（09）贪腐：官员贪污腐败，涉及农民、工人（国企）。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424201\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/贪腐.jpg\" alt=\"贪腐\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/贪腐.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/贪腐-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/贪腐-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/贪腐-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/贪腐-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（10）失业赔偿：工人被雇佣方解雇后、工厂倒闭导致工人失业后，雇佣方拒绝赔偿或者是赔偿金额过低，涉及工人。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424200\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失业赔偿.jpg\" alt=\"失业赔偿\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失业赔偿.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失业赔偿-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失业赔偿-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失业赔偿-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/失业赔偿-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（11）黑车：涉及出租车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424190\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/黑车.jpg\" alt=\"黑车\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/黑车.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/黑车-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/黑车-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/黑车-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/黑车-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（12）低薪：工资过低，要求加薪，涉及工人、教师、医护。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424188\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/低薪.jpg\" alt=\"低薪\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/低薪.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/低薪-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/低薪-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/低薪-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/低薪-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（13）租金：商城租金暴涨商户无力承担，涉及商户。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424206\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/租金.jpg\" alt=\"租金\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/租金.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/租金-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/租金-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/租金-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/租金-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（14）城管暴力：涉及路人。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424187\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/城管暴力.jpg\" alt=\"城管暴力\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/城管暴力.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/城管暴力-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/城管暴力-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/城管暴力-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/城管暴力-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（15）欠缴社保：雇佣方未缴纳（或未足额缴纳）被雇佣方的五险一金，涉及工人、教师、医护。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424194\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠缴社保.jpg\" alt=\"欠缴社保\" width=\"600\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠缴社保.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠缴社保-300x171.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠缴社保-768x438.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/欠缴社保-1024x585.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（16）克扣工资：雇佣方克扣被雇佣方的薪资、奖金等，涉及工人、教师、医护。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424193\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/克扣工资.jpg\" alt=\"克扣工资\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/克扣工资.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/克扣工资-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/克扣工资-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/克扣工资-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/克扣工资-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（17）规费：出租车公司向出租车收取的费用（也叫份子钱）太高，涉及出租车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424189\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/规费.jpg\" alt=\"规费\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/规费.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/规费-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/规费-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/规费-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/规费-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（18）搬迁赔偿：公司搬迁厂区但拒绝对受影响的工人作出赔偿（或赔偿过低），涉及工人。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424186\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/搬迁赔偿.jpg\" alt=\"搬迁赔偿\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/搬迁赔偿.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/搬迁赔偿-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/搬迁赔偿-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/搬迁赔偿-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/搬迁赔偿-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（19）运营权：运营权被政府强行收回，涉及出租车、公交车、客运车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424205\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运营权.jpg\" alt=\"运营权\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运营权.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运营权-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运营权-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运营权-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运营权-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（20）警察暴力：涉及路人。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424192\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/警察暴力.jpg\" alt=\"警察暴力\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/警察暴力.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/警察暴力-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/警察暴力-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/警察暴力-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/警察暴力-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>（21）运价：运价低要求涨价，涉及出租车、公交车、客运车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-424204\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运价.jpg\" alt=\"运价\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运价.jpg 1720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运价-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运价-768x447.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运价-1024x595.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/01/运价-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>备注：</p>\n<p>1）在我们收集到当天的图文资料的情况下，同一事件如持续到第二天或多天，算另一起或多起。</p>\n<p>2）我们的联系邮箱是：darkmamu2@gmail.com，推特账号是：@wickedonnaa ，博客1: http://newsworthknowingcn.blogspot.com 博客2: wickedonna.blogspot.com</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[8906,13804,26944]}